               <head>Igeret al tehi ke-avotekha by Profiat Duran</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070331" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Polemical treatise. </summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="17v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Igeret al tehi ke-avotekha</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אגרת אל תהי כאבותיך</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/13522985" xml:lang="en">Duran, Profiat, 1350-1415</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/13522985" xml:lang="he">דורן, יצחק בן משה, 1350-1415</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A satirical epistle addressed to David En-Bonet ben Goron, with the commentary of Joseph ben Shem Tov. The contents of the title page (folio 1r) are taken from the printed edition of Constatinople 1577, with some modifications by the scribe. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="he">[...] ועתה נתחדשה ותצא לאור משפטה בכתב יד הצעיר הכותב ה"ה <name type="person" role="scribe">יששכר חיים בלא"א יצחק קרפי</name> ז"ל בשנת י'ששכר' ל'פעו'לתך לפ"ק" [=תקמ"ו]. <locus n="1r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     </incipit>
                     
                     
                     
                     <decoNote type="border">
                        
                        
                        
                        <locus n="1r"/>Title-page in an ornamented frame, in black ink. </decoNote>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
               </msContents>
               
               
               
